ts can be lifted by increasing the\nnumber of extra dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2004 00:06:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2004 17:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
