 spin superalgebras which act on\nthe supersingleton and higher spin states in any dimension. For the cases of\n$AdS_3$, $AdS_4$, and $AdS_5$ the isomorphisms with the higher spin\nsuperalgebras defined earlier in terms of spinor generating elements are\nestablished.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2004 17:51:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2004 15:33:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2004 18:18:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 8 Feb 2005 18:10:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
